Chapter 1. Admin Guide

   Table of Contents

   1. Overview
   2. Installing the module
   3. Using the module
   4. Dependencies

        4.1. Kamailio Modules
        4.2. External Libraries or Applications

   5. Parameters

        5.1. filename (string)
        5.2. modpath (string)
        5.3. reset_cycles (int)
        5.4. perl_destroy_func (string)

   6. Functions

        6.1. perl_exec_simple(func, [param])
